text: == Events == * Count Henry I of Champagne marries Marie de Champagne. * Uppsala is recognized as the seat of the Swedish metropolitan. * Antipope Paschal III elected by cardinals supporting Frederick Barbarossa. * Olaf II of Norway is canonized as Saint Olaf. * Archbishop Rainald of Dassel brings relics of the Magi from Milan to Cologne. * Thomas Becket contends with Henry II, leaves England to solicit support from the Pope and the King of France. * The first written record of Tver Category:1164
